Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:52.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:57.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
