Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:15.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:22.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}いつまでも 手を振りたい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ここに たしかに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:32.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君といた証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:36.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ずっと スピラーレ
